# Horizontal curve creater

## Description

The Program has a switch (userInput) which by default is set to False . This will require no input from the user and run with default parameters.
If the switches state is changed it will ask the user for input.

The program makes use of he matplot library and therefore when it is run will open a new window showing the plotted points of the horizontal curve. The output will also shows all the joins / polars computed in order to get the end result.

## Output 

Shows chainage points and general shape of the road using matplot





